headline_print_headline: Have Yourself a Merry Little January

abstract: Henok Fentie, the Swedish craft brewer who runs one of the coolest bars in the city, shares his top spots in Sodermalm, the buzzy enclave where he grew up.
snippet: Henok Fentie, the Swedish craft brewer who runs one of the coolest bars in the city, shares his top spots in Sodermalm, the buzzy enclave where he grew up.
lead_paragraph: There’s more to the Swedish capital than its good looks. For proof, look south to Sodermalm, a large inner-city island humming with creativity. “There are more fun and innovative and exciting and heartfelt things going on in Sodermalm than anywhere else in Stockholm,” said the craft brewer Henok Fentie, a Stockholm native and co-founder of Omnipollo, an experimental, and highly influential, Swedish beer producer.

abstract: We make too much and buy too much. But maybe there is a way not to waste too much. The ragpicker of Brooklyn has an idea.
snippet: We make too much and buy too much. But maybe there is a way not to waste too much. The ragpicker of Brooklyn has an idea.
lead_paragraph: The ragpicker of Brooklyn works out of a 750-square-foot storefront a few blocks east of the Brooklyn-Queens Expressway, down a mostly residential side street in Williamsburg, where Hasidim and hipsters mix.

abstract: The streaming services have data on viewers’ spending habits and brand preferences, and they’re looking into new ways to use it.
snippet: The streaming services have data on viewers’ spending habits and brand preferences, and they’re looking into new ways to use it.
lead_paragraph: First came product placement. In exchange for a payment, whether in cash, supplies or services, a TV show or a film would prominently display a brand-name product.

abstract: Raise taxes? Cut state programs? Neither option is ever desirable, especially in a year when every state lawmaker is up for re-election.
snippet: Raise taxes? Cut state programs? Neither option is ever desirable, especially in a year when every state lawmaker is up for re-election.
lead_paragraph: For much of this year, it seemed that nothing could stand in the way of progressive activists’ agenda in New York. Not conservative backlash, not big money’s lobbying, not even Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo’s hesitations.

abstract: Felix Rohatyn was from a different era, when an ambitious rich man could be content to rescue a city and not run the world.
snippet: Felix Rohatyn was from a different era, when an ambitious rich man could be content to rescue a city and not run the world.
lead_paragraph: On Tuesday morning at Frank E. Campbell, the Madison Avenue funeral home, Michael R. Bloomberg (former mayor, current presidential candidate) delivered a eulogy in memory of Felix G. Rohatyn — banker, writer, urbanist, savior, mensch.

abstract: Dr. Stanley Forwand’s long search for a soul mate ended last year when he met Marjorie Barnes. Dr. Forwand, 84, and Ms. Barnes, 77, both can take a joke and dish them out, too.
snippet: Dr. Stanley Forwand’s long search for a soul mate ended last year when he met Marjorie Barnes. Dr. Forwand, 84, and Ms. Barnes, 77, both can take a joke and dish them out, too.
lead_paragraph: Dr. Stanley Forwand spent six consecutive years searching online for the perfect woman. During that time, he doled out thousands of dollars on airline tickets and drove his Toyota Prius more than 70,000 miles to the homes of women he had met on dating apps, hoping to find “a steady and sane, loving partner for life.”
